title: + WU Zhaohui Meets with TU/e Delegation [10-12-2015] (Zhejiang University)
text: ( Source : Zhejiang University ) Oct. 12, 2015 On October 8, WU Zhaohui, President of Zhejiang University, met with and held a friendly talk with a delegation of the Eindhoven University of Technology (TU/e) led by Prof. Frank Baaijens , Rector
